@DATABASE "Fall Guy"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - F - Fall Guy"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - F
                   ====================================

                                 Fall Guy
                                 ========


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(43896,2)"}          43896,2
@{"Level Cheat   " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(43539,0)"}          43539,0
@{"Infinite Bonus" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(43402,195) ZXAMPoke(43403,195)"}          43402,195:43403,195

                         Note:- The Infinite Lives POKE works by stopping the
                                game jumping to the Game Over part, so it looks
                                like you are losing your lives, but don't worry!

                                The "Level Cheat" is a way to completely spoil
                                the game. You only have to make one successful
                                jump to complete the level.
                                                             Rastan.
@endnode
